---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABanner from '../components/CTABanner.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services — Fractional CTO, AI Implementation, Funnel Engineering & Technology Consulting | Carlos Vargas"
  description="Fractional CTO services, AI implementation, funnel architecture, technology troubleshooting, and business coaching for non-technical founders. Hands-on expertise, not just strategy."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="hero-headline">Five Ways to Put CTO-Level Technology Expertise to Work in Your Business</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Every service is built around the same principle: technology should generate revenue, save time, and scale with your business. Not create complexity you have to manage.</p>
      <nav class="anchor-nav" aria-label="Services navigation">
        <a href="#fractional-cto">Fractional CTO</a>
        <a href="#ai-implementation">AI Implementation</a>
        <a href="#funnel-architecture">Funnel Architecture</a>
        <a href="#troubleshooting">Troubleshooting</a>
        <a href="#coaching">Coaching</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICE 1 -->
  <section class="service-section" id="fractional-cto">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Service 01</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Strategic Technology Leadership — Without the Full-Time Price Tag</h2>
      <div class="service-body">
        <p>Your business has reached the point where technology decisions have real consequences. A Fractional CTO gives you the strategic technology leadership your business needs at a fraction of the cost of a full-time executive hire. Carlos works as an embedded member of your leadership team — setting technology direction, evaluating vendors, making architectural decisions, and ensuring every technical investment connects to a business outcome.</p>
        <h3>Key Outcomes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Technology Roadmap</strong> — 90-day and 12-month plan aligned to your business goals</li>
          <li><strong>Architecture Decisions</strong> — Platform selection and integration strategy that scales</li>
          <li><strong>Vendor Evaluation</strong> — Objective assessment of every tool in your stack</li>
          <li><strong>Team Guidance</strong> — Technical leadership for your development team</li>
          <li><strong>Cost Optimization</strong> — Average 30-40% reduction in technology spend</li>
          <li><strong>Risk Mitigation</strong> — Security review, backup strategy, disaster recovery</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="engagement-model"><strong>Engagement:</strong> Monthly retainer, 10-20 hours/month, 3-month minimum.</p>
        <a href="/book-a-call/" class="btn-primary">Book a Strategy Call</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICE 2 -->
  <section class="service-section alt" id="ai-implementation">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Service 02</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Implement AI in Your Business in 90 Days — Without Writing Code</h2>
      <div class="service-body">
        <p>AI is the single largest operational advantage available to small and growing businesses right now. Carlos designs and implements AI-powered systems that automate your operations, accelerate your content production, and give you capabilities that would otherwise require hiring two or three additional team members.</p>
        <h3>Key Outcomes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>AI Readiness Assessment</strong> — Identify highest-impact AI opportunities</li>
          <li><strong>90-Day Implementation Roadmap</strong> — Phased plan with tools, timelines, and expected outcomes</li>
          <li><strong>Tool Selection &amp; Setup</strong> — Hands-on implementation of AI tools</li>
          <li><strong>Workflow Integration</strong> — Connect AI to your existing systems</li>
          <li><strong>Team Training</strong> — Practical training for independent operation</li>
          <li><strong>Performance Measurement</strong> — ROI tracking framework</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="service-ctas">
          <a href="/book-a-call/" class="btn-primary">Book a Call to Discuss AI</a>
          <a href="/resources/" class="btn-link">Take the AI Readiness Scorecard &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICE 3 -->
  <section class="service-section" id="funnel-architecture">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Service 03</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Funnels That Convert Traffic Into Revenue — Engineered, Not Guessed</h2>
      <div class="service-body">
        <p>A funnel is an engineered system — a sequence of pages, emails, automations, and conversion points that work together to turn a stranger into a buyer. Carlos approaches funnel building the way an engineer approaches a system: with a clear architecture, tested integrations, and measurable performance at every stage.</p>
        <h3>Key Outcomes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Funnel Architecture Design</strong> — Complete blueprint including page flow and automation sequences</li>
          <li><strong>Page Build &amp; Technical Setup</strong> — Landing pages, sales pages, order forms — built and tested</li>
          <li><strong>Integration Engineering</strong> — Payment processors, CRM, email automation, analytics — all connected</li>
          <li><strong>Email Automation</strong> — Welcome, cart abandonment, post-purchase, and nurture sequences</li>
          <li><strong>A/B Testing Framework</strong> — Specific hypotheses for optimization</li>
          <li><strong>Conversion Optimization</strong> — Data-driven iteration on real metrics</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/book-a-call/" class="btn-primary">Book a Call to Discuss Your Funnel</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICE 4 -->
  <section class="service-section alt" id="troubleshooting">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Service 04</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">When Your Technology Breaks, You Need Someone Who Can Fix It — Fast</h2>
      <div class="service-body">
        <p>Something is broken and it is costing you money right now. Carlos provides rapid-response technology troubleshooting and integration repair. This is not a help desk — this is a Solutions Architect who diagnoses the root cause, implements the fix, and restructures the integration so it does not break again.</p>
        <h3>Key Outcomes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Rapid Diagnostics</strong> — Root-cause analysis of broken integrations and system errors</li>
          <li><strong>Emergency Repair</strong> — Priority fix for revenue-critical systems</li>
          <li><strong>Integration Rebuild</strong> — Restructure with proper error handling and failover</li>
          <li><strong>Platform Migration</strong> — Move between platforms without losing data or revenue</li>
          <li><strong>System Audit</strong> — Complete review with prioritized fix list</li>
          <li><strong>Documentation</strong> — Clear docs so your team can maintain systems</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="engagement-model"><strong>Engagement:</strong> Project-based. Can begin within 24-48 hours for urgent issues.</p>
        <a href="/book-a-call/" class="btn-primary">Get Help Within 48 Hours</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICE 5 -->
  <section class="service-section" id="coaching">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Service 05</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Build Your Technology Confidence — Not Just Your Technology Stack</h2>
      <div class="service-body">
        <p>Some founders do not need someone to build for them. They need someone to build with them. Carlos's coaching combines deep technical knowledge with business strategy and founder psychology. This is a CTO sitting across the table from you, teaching you the reasoning behind each decision so you can make those decisions independently.</p>
        <h3>Key Outcomes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>1:1 Coaching Sessions</strong> — Weekly or biweekly, focused on your challenges</li>
          <li><strong>Decision Frameworks</strong> — Reusable frameworks for evaluating tools, platforms, and vendors</li>
          <li><strong>AI Literacy</strong> — Practical understanding specific to your business</li>
          <li><strong>Technology Confidence</strong> — Informed conversations with developers and agencies</li>
          <li><strong>Accountability</strong> — Structured goals with measurable progress</li>
          <li><strong>Resource Library</strong> — Access to playbooks, templates, and implementation guides</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="engagement-model"><strong>Engagement:</strong> Monthly, biweekly 60-minute sessions with async support. 3-month minimum recommended.</p>
        <a href="/book-a-call/" class="btn-primary">Apply for Coaching</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER CTA -->
  <CTABanner
    headline="Not Sure Which Service Is Right for Your Business?"
    body="Start with a conversation. Every engagement begins with a 30-minute strategy call where Carlos assesses your situation and recommends the right path forward."
    secondaryCta="Or start with the AI Readiness Scorecard"
    secondaryHref="/resources/"
  />

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a1628 0%, #0f2440 100%);
  }

  .hero-headline {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }

  .anchor-nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .anchor-nav a {
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }

  .anchor-nav a:hover {
    border-color: #2dd4bf;
    color: #2dd4bf;
  }

  .service-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-section.alt {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
  }

  .service-body {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .service-body p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-body h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #2dd4bf;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .service-body ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .service-body li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .service-body li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.85rem;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #2dd4bf;
  }

  .engagement-model {
    font-size: 0.9375rem !important;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55) !important;
    border-left: 3px solid rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.3);
    padding-left: 1rem !important;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    background: #2dd4bf;
    color: #0a1628;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #5eead4;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .service-ctas {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-link {
    color: #2dd4bf;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .btn-link:hover {
    color: #5eead4;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-headline {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .service-section {
      padding: 3rem 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
